{{!
    @template mod_book/view_book

    View book page.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * navigationclass string The navigation css class.
    * navigation string The HTML of the data requests table.
    * chaptertitle string The title of the chapter.
    * chaptersubtitle string The title of the subchapter.
    * chaptertext string The content text of the chapter.
    * taglist string The HTML of the list of the chapter's related tags.
    * chapterclass string The chapter css class.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "navigationclass": "navtext",
        "navigation": "<a title='Next' class='booknext' href='#'></a>",
        "chaptertitle": "Chapter title",
        "chaptersubtitle": "Subchapter title",
        "chaptertext": "Chapter text",
        "taglist": "<div class='tag_list'></div>",
        "chapterclass": "dimmed_text"
    }
}}
